#Changing the Date and Target feature(MW) to 'ds' and 'y' to Train the model as per FBProphet.

    .rename(columns={'datetime_beginning_ept':'ds',
                     'mw':'y'})

    .rename(columns={'datetime_beginning_ept':'ds',
                     'mw':'y'})

    .rename(columns={'datetime_beginning_ept':'ds',

In [25]:
def mean_absolute_percentage_error(y_true, y_pred): 
    """Calculates MAPE given y_true and y_pred"""
    y_true, y_pred = np.array(y_true), np.array(y_pred)
    return np.mean(np.abs((y_true - y_pred) / y_true)) * 100

mean_absolute_percentage_error(y_true=pjme_w_test['mw'],
                   y_pred=forecast_w_test['yhat'])
